                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14662263" author="carlyeks" created="Fri, 7 Aug 2015 18:55:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Good catch. It is caused by &lt;tt&gt;MaterializedView.updateAffectsView()&lt;/tt&gt;; this was due to a change in the way &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-8099&quot; title=&quot;Refactor and modernize the storage engine&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-8099&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-8099&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; handled CQL row deletions which wasn&apos;t properly captured in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6477&quot; title=&quot;Materialized Views (was: Global Indexes)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-6477&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-6477&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve pushed &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/carlyeks/cassandra/tree/ticket/10014&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;a branch&lt;/a&gt; that contains a fix for this.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14680256" author="tjake" created="Mon, 10 Aug 2015 15:24:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 committed, thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
